{"title":"陈企霞遗诗二首","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":6,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈企霞遗诗二首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几经锒铛入囹圄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狱卒残狡难友怒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙塔桃花风雨中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丹忱总似贯日虹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少年意气输自量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快马飞驰奔疆场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书生胸怀战士胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思尽绵薄斩楼兰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天旋地转神州晓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗众拥处处飘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豪情满怀天安门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窃幸终不虚此生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秃笔夜夜伴孤灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当时文坛曾侧身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滥竽愧难狮子吼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细心甘为蚕儿缯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身困三厄烟茶酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目迷五色敌我友。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原非自弃甘沉沦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢待曙色升赤球！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖畔盘桓十五年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋月春晓谁为伴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最是风雨亭畔过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少英豪叹蹉跎！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老病已多只欠死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜嗔皆尽惟余痴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（借人两句）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江山锦绣何等好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂无惭疚度黄昏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七七·旧历"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月下旬，我生日将到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杂感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山水水皆诗情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人我我亦经花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豪情耐磨我竟老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耻叹世路常蹲蹬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少慕相如真勇敢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以弱敌强懦颜汗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老薄方朔太谄媚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打小帮大饰肤浅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汉刘意兴歌大风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魏武才调吟短歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最是李杜多绝响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗坛代代仰正宗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大块文章非我有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百代过客复何求。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劝君更尽一杯酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与尔同销万古愁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（集古二句）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钟情耽读易安词，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤愤常掩东坡诗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最是李白放狂歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敞我胸怀呼荷荷。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}